# One person per line:   id   telegram_bot_token   [gonka_key]
#
#   id                 1-20 lowercase letters/digits — used in the container name
#                      (hermes-<id>) and the web subdomain (hermes-<id>.DOMAIN)
#   telegram_bot_token from @BotFather, ONE bot per person (one token = one poller).
#                      Leave blank for web-only access.
#   gonka_key          OPTIONAL. Omit to use the shared GONKA_API_KEY from ../.env.
#                      One shared key is fine for ~5 people; give heavy users or a
#                      bigger team their own key for separate rate limits + billing.
#
# copy this file to team/team.users and edit.

